reviews: Really easy to clean and great colour! Makes baking fun! I also bought the matching icing spatula.
I love the design and colour! Works well and easy to hand wash.
Big blue balloons. Look really cute!

review_title: I wouldn't recommend the case, but I still use it
reviews: It's a durable case in protecting your phone and I really like the piece to use as a stand for watching YouTube or Netflix. The only downfall is the coating on the case scratches off easily. I've just scratched it all off, so that it's one even colour. It's more of a lighter pink. I'm not sure why they bother with the top coating as it doesn't stay on.

review_title: I love this classic tarot deck with the muted colours
reviews: Great quality cards and I loved the additional illustrations that came along with the deck. Would highly recommend!

I use this on little travel adventures when I can't bring the letterbox in. Haven't tried while flying yet. I bring a ziplock bag of litter with me to fill when needed for the box. It's somewhat easy to empty out, except the sides start collapsing on you as you do, so it takes finesse. Cleans easy enough. I do like that it folds up after.
Fits comfortably and looks cool. Keeps my head warm while I'm at it.

review_title: Great little pots with holes for plants
reviews: I bought these for some small plants I've taken cuttings for and they're perfect! Glad they have a decent size drainage hole and a bottom tray.
Great pen, but didn’t need the magnet. Seems kind of wasteful.
Great book! Can’t wait to use it.

I've changed my review since growing the AeroGarden herbs for a couple of months now. My parsley grew wonderfully, the oregano has only produced one stem and there have been only four mature leaves on it. They brown and die typically, but I'm still hoping he'll pull through. The basil was wonderful, but the seeds have been mixed. I ordered Italian herbs and one of the basil stems is a Thai basil.
My cat doesn't find it as interesting as I hoped.
We went up half a size on purchase, but definitely needed a full size up.
